T. D. Crittenden https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/T._D._Crittenden 0 T. D. Crittenden (September 27, 1878 – February 17, 1938) was an American actor of the silent era. He appeared in 69 films between 1912 and 1924. He was born in Oakland, California and died in Los Angeles, California.
